title: GORGEOUS VIEW FROM MARQUIZ RESIDENCE!!!
posting_body: ['Marquis Residences.', 'Yearly lease only, Furnished or unfurnished, or owner can add/remove furniture.', 'Enjoy stunning views of Biscayne Bay, Miami Beach & The Atlantic Ocean Day or Night!', 'The unit offers private elevator entry, Marquis Residences is located in the heart of Miami just steps from Museum Park, Bayside, South Beach, Midtown, & Brickell.', 'Marquis offers top of the line amenities such as pool, spa, Jacuzzi, hotel and much more!', 'Great location at amazing price!', "Don't miss out!", 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
